description:
This test case performs the following steps:
1. Navigate to the Swoop.ge site.
2. Click on the movie section button.
3. Select the first movie available in east point.
4. Click on the last date available.
5. Check that all available options are 'East Point' .
6. Click on the last available option.
7. Verify movie details such as name, date, and cinema.
8. Click on a vacant seat.
